org.springframework.cloud.gcp.pubsub.support

Class AcknowledgeablePubsubMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.cloud.gcp.pubsub.support.AcknowledgeablePubsubMessage

  • public class AcknowledgeablePubsubMessage
extends Object
    A PubsubMessage wrapper that allows it to be acknowledged.

    To acknowledge AcknowledgeablePubsubMessage in bulk, using a PubSubOperations.ack(java.util.Collection) is recommended. To do that, a user must first extract the ack IDs and group them by subscription name.

    Author:
    João André Martins
